Text: Relax, bro I simply asked why all the tracks weren't on the upload you made of the remastered version of that album. Those are some good songs. I don't know why you would not include them. If I happen to download anything in the future from you THANKS!!!

"relax" is my middle name.... 

I'm not much for material that didn't make the final release.  If it wasn't good enough for the Artist then I'd prefer not to listen to it either.

Happy Listening!
